{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"event.isChar","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/isChar","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/detail\"><code>detail</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/sourceCapabilities\"><code>sourceCapabilities</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/view\"><code>view</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/which\"><code>which</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/initUIEvent\"><code>initUIEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/initUIEvent\"><code>initUIEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n <strong>警告：</strong> 不要使用该属性，该属性有一个已知的 bug，就是它始终返回<code>false</code>,从不返回<code>true</code>.查看<a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=312552\" title=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=312552\" rel=\" noopener\">https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=312552</a></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"概述","isH3":true,"content":"<p>返回一个布尔值，表明该事件是否是由一个字符按键触发的。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">bool = event.isChar\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例子","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"> if(e.isChar){\n   echoInput(e.type);\n }\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"备注","isH3":true,"content":"<p>一些常用的组合键可能会触发键盘事件，但是不会产生任何字符 (例如:CTRL + ALT + ?).在这种情况下，isChar 返回 false.isChar 常用于判断用户在一个文本输入框内输入的是否为一个字符。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"规范","isH3":true,"content":"<p>不属于任何公开的规范</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"返回一个布尔值，表明该事件是否是由一个字符按键触发的。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"event.isChar","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/uievent/ischar","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/uievent/ischar/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent","title":"UIEvent"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/isChar","title":"event.isChar"}],"pageTitle":"event.isChar - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}